---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About | HosDev">
  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>About HosDev</h1>
    
    <p>
      HosDev is a modern development platform specifically designed for the hospitality industry. Our mission is to empower hotels, resorts, and other accommodation providers with the tools they need to thrive in today's digital landscape.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>
      We envision a future where hospitality businesses of all sizes can leverage cutting-edge technology without requiring extensive technical expertise or prohibitive investments. By providing a comprehensive, accessible platform, we aim to level the playing field and enable innovation across the industry.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
    <p>
      Having worked in both the hospitality and technology sectors, we've witnessed firsthand the challenges that arise when these worlds collide. Many existing solutions are either too complex, too expensive, or simply not designed with the specific needs of hospitality professionals in mind.
    </p>
    <p>
      HosDev was born from the desire to bridge this gap. We've built a platform that combines powerful functionality with intuitive design, all tailored specifically for the unique requirements of hospitality businesses.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Core Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> Technology should make life easier, not more complicated. We design with simplicity in mind.</li>
      <li><strong>Adaptability:</strong> Every business is unique. Our platform is flexible enough to adapt to different operational models.</li>
      <li><strong>Security:</strong> We prioritize the security of your data and your guests' information.</li>
      <li><strong>Support:</strong> We're committed to providing exceptional support throughout your journey with us.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Get Started</h2>
    <p>
      Whether you're running a boutique hotel, a large resort, or anything in between, HosDev has the tools you need to streamline operations and enhance guest experiences. 
    </p>
    <p>
      Interested in learning more? Contact us to schedule a demo or explore our documentation to get started.
    </p>
    
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="/docs" class="btn btn-outline">Explore Docs</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: var(--width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  ul {
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
    
    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>